PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773321080
OL,3,CFoodbank charity warns hunger
OL,4,C'continues to grip communities'
OL,6,FAssistant manager Paul Harris says
OL,7,Fnumbers have stayed at a high level at
OL,8,FSalford Foodbank.
OL,10,FHunger is continuing to grip
OL,11,Fcommunities, according to a foodbank
OL,12,Fcharity as it revealed that almost
OL,13,F300,000 emergency parcels were given
OL,14,Fto people facing hunger and hardship
OL,15,Facross the North West in 2025.
OL,17,FTrussell says it provided the
OL,18,Fequivalent of 820 food parcels a day
OL,19,Fin the region - the equivalent of one
OL,20,Fevery two minutes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773321080
OL,3,CFoodbank charity warns hunger
OL,4,C'continues to grip communities'
OL,6,FThe number of emergency food parcels
OL,7,Fprovided in the North West last year
OL,8,Fis 22% higher than before the pandemic
OL,9,Fand cost of living crisis, it added.
OL,11,FHelen Barnard, director of policy and
OL,12,Fresearch at Trussell, said: "Today's
OL,13,Ffigures show that too many people
OL,14,Facross the North West are still being
OL,15,Fpushed to the brink.
OL,17,F"Too many people are being forced to
OL,18,Fskip meals so their children can eat,
OL,19,For survive on cups of tea because they
OL,20,Fdon't have any food left in the
OL,21,Fcupboards.
OL,26,@tD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773321080
OL,3,CFoodbank charity warns hunger
OL,4,C'continues to grip communities'
OL,6,F"The pandemic and cost of living
OL,7,Fcrisis have left deep scars. Severe
OL,8,Fhardship still weighs heavily on daily
OL,9,Flives, leaving people feeling
OL,10,Foverlooked and left behind."
OL,12,FThe charity said incomes from social
OL,13,Fsecurity and wages are failing to
OL,14,Fcover the costs of food, utility bills
OL,15,Fand other essentials like toiletries
OL,16,Ffor many families.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773321080
OL,3,CFoodbank charity warns hunger
OL,4,C'continues to grip communities'
OL,6,FParents are among the people
OL,7,Fshouldering the heaviest burden as
OL,8,Ffamilies with children in North West
OL,9,Freceived 61% of all parcels in 2025,
OL,10,Fdespite making up just 42% of the
OL,11,Fregion's population.
OL,13,FTrussell said there was an "alarming
OL,14,Frise in hardship" among older people
OL,15,Fin the region, with the number of
OL,16,Fparcels provided to support people
OL,17,Faged 65 and over in 2025 more than two
OL,18,Fand a half times (+159%) the level in
OL,19,F2019.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773321080
OL,3,CFoodbank charity warns hunger
OL,4,C'continues to grip communities'
OL,6,FBosses at Widnes Foodbank warned that
OL,7,Fthey are under pressure as donation
OL,8,Flevels are not keeping pace with the
OL,9,Flevels of need.
OL,11,FProject co-ordinator Vicky Ferguson
OL,12,Fsaid, "Every day at Widnes Foodbank we
OL,13,Fmeet people facing hunger who are
OL,14,Fstruggling to get by.
OL,16,F"We are here to provide support,
OL,17,Fadvice and emergency food, but it
OL,18,Fshouldn't have to be this way.
OL,19,FFoodbanks are not a long-term solution.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773321080
OL,3,CFoodbank charity warns hunger
OL,4,C'continues to grip communities'
OL,6,F"We need the government to put better
OL,7,Fsupport systems in place for people
OL,8,Fwho are struggling with the costs of
OL,9,Fessentials and the challenging
OL,10,Frealities of everyday life ` such as
OL,11,Fsocial security payments, insecure
OL,12,Fhousing, job loss or the impact of
OL,13,Fhealth conditions and disability."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773321080
OL,3,CFoodbank charity warns hunger
OL,4,C'continues to grip communities'
OL,6,F"We are deeply grateful for all the
OL,7,Fgenerous support we receive from our
OL,8,Flocal community. If you are able, we
OL,9,Fwould encourage you to play your part
OL,10,Fby donating food or funds to your
OL,11,Flocal foodbank to ensure everyone is
OL,12,Fsupported and no-one faces hunger
OL,13,Falone in the North West."
OL,15,FThe government has previously said
OL,16,Fthat it is helping with everyday costs
OL,17,Fby increasing the National Minimum
OL,18,FWage, taking #150 off energy bills
OL,19,Ffrom April and recommitting to the
OL,20,FTriple Lock.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773321080
OL,3,CFoodbank charity warns hunger
OL,4,C'continues to grip communities'
OL,6,FAcross the UK, Trussell reported a 12%
OL,7,Fdrop in the total parcel numbers
OL,8,Fcompared to 2024, which it attributed
OL,9,Fto easing inflation and fewer people
OL,10,Flosing their jobs.
OL,12,FBut Ms Barnard added, "Slowing price
OL,13,Frises alone cannot solve the scale of
OL,14,Fsevere hardship still facing our
OL,15,Fcommunities. And as we face uncertain
OL,16,Ftimes again, progress can be too
OL,17,Feasily undone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773321080
OL,3,CFoodbank charity warns hunger
OL,4,C'continues to grip communities'
OL,6,F"Even as we gain hope from people
OL,7,Fgetting back on their feet, we cannot
OL,8,Flose sight of the heartbreaking
OL,9,Finjustice that such shocking numbers
OL,10,Fof people are still trapped in the
OL,11,Fgrip of severe hardship."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
